Regularization:
  Objective: L_total = L_task + 1.0 * R_perp + 3.0 * R_sparse
  Concurvity (Siems et al. 2023, arXiv:2305.11475, NeurIPS 2023):
    lambda_concurvity = 1.0
    R_perp = (1/K) * sum_k  mean_{i<j} |Corr(f_{i,k}(X_i), f_{j,k}(X_j))|
    (multiclass avg over K=7 classes; Pearson corr over batch dim)
  Group LASSO sparsity (Xu et al. 2022, arXiv:2202.12482, ICLR 2022):
    lambda_sparsity = 3.0
    R_sparse = sum_{i=1}^{p} ||theta_i||_2  (L2 norm of each sub-network group)
    zero_threshold = 0.0001
    Sparsity method: proximal gradient descent — exact group zeroing (Xu et al. 2022)

